        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shisanjing/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4150490-11.jpg" alt="南渡錄" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27475501/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27475501/" class="">第10冊82頁</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shisanjing/" class=" " title="南渡錄">南渡錄</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27475501">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">《高宗純皇帝實錄》卷67，乾隆三年四月甲辰條：禮部議准，陝西道御史八時疏言：繙譯鄉試內簾，止將擬取之硃卷進呈，毋庸取閱墨卷，至發榜時始將墨卷公同拆名，從之。按此人名應作八時泰，《實錄》脫一字。一檔館藏錄副奏摺03-1163-033號即其原摺抄件，乾隆三年三月十五日上，奉硃批“該部議奏”。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-07 21:03</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                《高宗純皇帝實錄》卷67，乾隆三年四月甲辰條：<blockquote><q>禮部議准，陝西道御史八時疏言：繙譯鄉試內簾，止將擬取之硃卷進呈，毋庸取閱墨卷，至發榜時始將墨卷公同拆名，從之。</q></blockquote>按此人名應作八時泰，《實錄》脫一字。一檔館藏錄副奏摺03-1163-033號即其原摺抄件，乾隆三年三月十五日上，奉硃批“該部議奏”。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
